</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/Ddb9kD-HyPc" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/10/12/ios-15-0-2-and-ipados-15-0-2-released-time-to-update-your-iphone/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=ios-15-0-2-and-ipados-15-0-2-released-time-to-update-your-iphone</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>傳 Google 推 Pixel Pass　新訂閱組合挑戰 Apple One</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/fqaJXN5PhDQ/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 12 Oct 2021 07:18:05 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple One]]></category><category><![CDATA[google]]></category><category><![CDATA[Pixel Pass]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1065196</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 去年推出 Apple One 訂閱組合，一次囊括 Apple Music、Apple TV Pl [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 去年推出 Apple One 訂閱組合，一次囊括 Apple Music、Apple TV Plus、Apple Arcade 和 Apple News Plus 等多種服務，對用家而言更方便、更優惠。近日有消息指，Google 亦有意跟進，將推出名為「Pixel Pass」的訂閱組合。</span></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Official Color names are:</p><p>Pixel 6 (Great Value)<br />&#8211; Kinda Coral<br />&#8211; Sorta Seafoam<br />&#8211; Stormy Black</p><p>Pixel 6 Pro (Flagship) &#8211; 512GB Max<br />&#8211; Sorta Sunny<br />&#8211; Cloudy White<br />&#8211; Stormy Black</p><p>Notice the framing: Value/Flagship. Makes sense to have the price gap $849/$1099.<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/pixel6?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#pixel6</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/teampixel?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#teampixel</a> <a href="https://t.co/YDIyXPP3pt">pic.twitter.com/YDIyXPP3pt</a></p><p>&mdash; M. Brandon Lee | THIS IS TECH TODAY (@thisistechtoday) <a href="https://twitter.com/thisistechtoday/status/1447248486877913089?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 10, 2021</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">據 Twitter 上的外洩情報可見，現時新訂閱服務價格未定，但應將透過 Google Fi 和 Google Store ，與購買 Pixel 設備一起銷售，Pixel 6 系列的顧客可直接訂閱 YouTube Premium 或 YouTube Music、Google One、Play Pass 和 Google Fi。相比單獨訂閱，若用家原先就是 Google 旗下服務的慣常用戶，訂閱服務應是划算得多。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1065197" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/A0F87616-7DF6-4DC6-9882-288558B96815-694x335.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="335" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/A0F87616-7DF6-4DC6-9882-288558B96815-694x335.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/A0F87616-7DF6-4DC6-9882-288558B96815-768x371.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/A0F87616-7DF6-4DC6-9882-288558B96815.jpeg 1205w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">雖目前暫未確定 Pixel Pass 訂閱方案所包含的內容及其具體價格，但就提供的服務涵蓋範圍來看，應優先以美國地區為主。Google 將於本月 20 日凌晨一點舉行線上發表會，目前已知 Google Pixel 6 及 Pixel 6 Pro 會在當日正式登台。據傳 Pixel 6 的價格在美國售價可能為 $749 美元（約港幣 5834 元）、Pixel 6 Pro 為 $1,049/1,099 美元（約港幣 8171 元 / 港幣 8561 元）。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/thisistechtoday/status/1447248486877913089?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1447248490321514500%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es2_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inside.com.tw%2Farticle%2F25157-google-pixel-pass">Twitter</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
